225
00:12:47,559 --> 00:12:50,338
And then we get into sort of the rarer types.

226
00:12:50,345 --> 00:12:54,498
About a third of people will see actual text or a sentence written there

227
00:12:54,559 --> 00:12:59,799
but when you try to read it, it doesn't make sense,
and there's a variant to that with musical notation.

228
00:12:59,799 --> 00:13:04,000
We don't know what's special about that type of 
object but that seems to be a typical

229
00:13:04,000 --> 00:13:05,919
Charles Bonnet syndrome hallucination.

230
00:13:05,919 --> 00:13:09,720
