269
00:16:24,799 --> 00:16:28,976
[ ♪ SOFT SYNTH MUSIC STARTS ♪ ]
I began to share and tell people more of you.

270
00:16:29,001 --> 00:16:32,255
And as I did, you became a part of me.

271
00:16:33,039 --> 00:16:38,559
I learned about you.
I found out who you were and why you existed.

272
00:16:39,080 --> 00:16:43,120
[ ♪ PERCUSSION MUSIC BUILDS ♪ ]
Do you have any idea how hard it is

273
00:16:43,120 --> 00:16:48,720
to tell those that you love, that you have been
terrified out of your wits all your life  

274
00:16:48,720 --> 00:16:51,000
and haven't been able to tell them.

275
00:16:51,000 --> 00:16:55,759
You bully and intimidate and like bullies the world over.

276
00:16:55,759 --> 00:17:01,519
Once you are exposed yourselves,
you weaken, you diminish.

277
00:17:02,000 --> 00:17:08,279
NINA: A breath, a moment, a thought,
and I am in control again.

278
00:17:08,279 --> 00:17:13,480
There are the times we get along,
and this is where you show your fun side

279
00:17:13,480 --> 00:17:17,279
with bubbles, stars, and plenty of colour.

280
00:17:17,920 --> 00:17:23,240
I own you. I'm going to tell as many people
about you as I can  

281
00:17:23,240 --> 00:17:30,240
in the hope that less people have to spend their 
lives trapped inside their own heads with you.

282
00:17:31,240 --> 00:17:36,279
I want to take what I've learnt from my life with you

283
00:17:36,279 --> 00:17:40,559
in the hope that it will teach others and help them.

284
00:17:42,359 --> 00:17:45,519
MILES: In short, your days are numbered.

285
00:17:45,519 --> 00:17:48,279
You will be understood

286
00:17:48,279 --> 00:17:50,079
and with understanding  

287
00:17:50,079 --> 00:17:52,960
comes acceptance and ownership

288
00:17:52,965 --> 00:17:56,925
and with acceptance and ownership comes freedom.

289
00:17:57,566 --> 00:18:01,440
[ ♪ MUSIC STOPS ♪ ]
NINA: On that note, Charles Bonnet syndrome, I thank you.

290
00:18:01,440 --> 00:18:03,960
 I am not so scared anymore. 

